{
  "stem": "21013.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I saw thousands of people fall to their knees and greeting him with flowers, with kisses.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there seemed to be no ill will.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It-- he was welcomed with open arms, although Schuschnigg made a speech as Hitler was crossing the border.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But it was all arranged beforehand, because Schuschnigg the chancellor had gone to Berchtesgarden.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There was a meeting there and Schuschnigg had to accept a Nazi into his government in Vienna.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "His name was Seyss-Inquart.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And that was sort of a quisling.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And it was all arranged.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The Anschluss was all arranged beforehand.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Schuschnigg was very weak.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he couldn't resist, because he didn't expect or get any help from the-- from England or France.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We had hoped that in the last minute somebody would come to our aid, but nobody did.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it affected me that we got thrown out of school, that the people that owed my father money in the stores, nobody paid.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Everybody took merchandise, bought it, and never paid.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We desperately tried to get out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I tried to get out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "A couple of my friends and I spent every single day going from one consulate to another to try to find a way of getting out or-- and find out the regulations that you had to follow to get a visa to another country.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We found out that you couldn't come to America, which was my first choice, because I thought that Broadway was paved with gold and there was a dollar print waiting for me at every corner, and I was looking for that.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And my parents were going to go to Israel to join my father's sister.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I also had an uncle in Alexandria, Egypt.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they tried to get my parents to get to Israel.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
